# Queen L.

Queen L.  (born 21 May 1986) was a chestnut Standardbred trotter by Crowntron out of Attila L. by Tibur.
Her most prestigious victories include the Swedish Trotting Derby (Swedish: Svenskt Travderby) (1990), Prix d'Am√©rique (1993) and Prix de France (1995). At the end of her career, the mare had earned US$2,383,158.
